summary: ...DISTURBANCE EXPECTED TO BECOME A TROPICAL STORM OVER THE WEEKEND... ...SIGNIFICANT RAINFALL EXPECTED OVER PORTIONS OF EASTERN CUBA AND THE BAHAMAS... As of 11:00 PM EDT Fri Sep 26 the center of Nine was located near 21.5, -76.0 with movement NW at 9 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1007 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 35 mph.
